### Test Cashier API Endpoints

### 1. Get Dashboard Stats
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cashier/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 2. Get Approved Orders
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cashier/approved-orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. Get Transactions
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cashier/transactions
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Get Transactions with Filters
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cashier/transactions?status=completed&paymentMethod=cash
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Get Financial Report
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cashier/financial-report?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-01-31
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
